Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:10.71,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直響著的沉默的警鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:12.93,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是誰的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:15.53,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳進去跳進去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:17.89,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起來 破壞掉這無理的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:19.48,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不開這沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:21.90,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:24.23,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到終幕我都要說
